  6. Import Issues: Missing Stubs (22 errors)

  What MyPy is teaching us:
  [import-not-found] errors for libraries suggest missing type stubs.

  Examples:
  - httpx.TestClient - httpx needs type stubs installed
  - utils.secure_command_execution - internal module might be outdated

  Architectural lesson: "Type ecosystem needs maintenance"
  - Install type stubs: poetry add --group dev types-httpx
  - Remove imports for archived/deleted modules

